  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Define position, displacement, and distance traveled.</item>
<item>Calculate the total displacement given the position as a function of time.</item>
<item>Determine the total distance traveled.</item>
<item>Calculate the average velocity given the displacement and elapsed time.</item>
</list></md:abstract>
